i\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁唔只係得audit位嘅<br />\nibgm起碼係advisory個d啦"},{"pid":"76490c32c9e661d18bbf63169b75e1a6427567c0","tid":480541,"uid":17232,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T10:53:46.000Z","msg":"霸佔完學位霸佔職位，現在霸佔床位，遲一些連靈位也想霸佔，中國人真是很霸道"},{"pid":"1976f135f63d2bcd861960513adcfb5ca1e86a04","tid":480541,"uid":35870,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T10:55:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有北大都唔讀走黎香港<br />\n<br />\n垃圾</blockquote><br />\n又話祖國很強大，又走落黎落後的香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f2f30ddee353d6addb65611825f21c5a31f40e","tid":480541,"uid":71133,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T10:58:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>狀元入big4做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁唔只係得audit位嘅<br />\nibgm起碼係advisory個d啦</blockquote><br />\n對連登仔黎講fg冇50k都係做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a71c02f4ed0d5dcf69bcd1d4fe78b4a2579179d","tid":480541,"uid":31389,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:00:38.000Z","msg":"連登廢柴又開始咬人喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814c864739ee426c688a83754a6c02e4a583d672","tid":480541,"uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:03:45.000Z","msg":"女auditor=..."}]}